{"tid":1980850,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[被控你會舒服晒嗎] 李柱銘：終可與優秀青年人齊走民主路","createTime":"2020-04-20T10:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T19:58:35.000Z","uid":167802,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4a8006d4dfc76ce71c2399ea7712596c99dd3548","tid":1980850,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T10:32:36.000Z","msg":"【4.18 大搜捕】歷來首被落案起訴 李柱銘：舒服晒，終可與優秀青年人齊走民主路<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/4-18-%E5%A4%A7%E6%90%9C%E6%8D%95-%E6%AD%B7%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E8%A2%AB%E8%90%BD%E6%A1%88%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4-%E6%9D%8E%E6%9F%B1%E9%8A%98-%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D%E6%99%92-%E7%B5%82%E5%8F%AF%E8%88%87%E5%84%AA%E7%A7%80%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E9%BD%8A%E8%B5%B0%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E8%B7%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F4-18-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2590%259C%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BE%2586%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A1%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%259F%25B1%25E9%258A%2598-%25E8%2588%2592%25E6%259C%258D%25E6%2599%2592-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2584%25AA%25E7%25A7%2580%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25BD%258A%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25B7%25AF%2F&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=59333305\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F4-18-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2590%259C%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BE%2586%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A1%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%259F%25B1%25E9%258A%2598-%25E8%2588%2592%25E6%259C%258D%25E6%2599%2592-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2584%25AA%25E7%25A7%2580%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25BD%258A%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25B7%25AF%2F&h=b6c5243b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/4-18-%E5%A4%A7%E6%90%9C%E6%8D%95-%E6%AD%B7%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E8%A2%AB%E8%90%BD%E6%A1%88%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4-%E6%9D%8E%E6%9F%B1%E9%8A%98-%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D%E6%99%92-%E7%B5%82%E5%8F%AF%E8%88%87%E5%84%AA%E7%A7%80%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E9%BD%8A%E8%B5%B0%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E8%B7%AF/</a><br />\n<br />\n我尊重佢係一位為民主奮戰多年嘅老人家<br />\n望住咁多位義士嘅犧牲，自己無被捕嘅心情一定好難受<br />\n<br />\n不過我好驚呢個變成好多人嘅心態<br />\n被控只係民主抗爭運動必有嘅一個現象而唔係目的<br />\n而家唔係鬥慘大會<br />\n運動裡面必然有人會做最大犧牲<br />\n有人能夠<strong>相對地</strong>坐享其成<br />\n<br />\n每日反省<br />\n保持理性<br />\n搵倒自己嘅崗位<br />\n至死方休<br />\n適量愧疚感可以作為推動力<br />\n偶爾受苦，可以短暫容許自己享受被釋放嘅罪疚感<br />\n但要做真正堅強，比對家更堅強嘅人<br />\n一定唔可以畀愧疚感主宰自己<br />\n比起必死嘅決心<br />\n更加需要面對負面情緒嘅勇氣<br />\n因為如果我係對家，見倒咁多人只係單純畀罪疚感折磨，而唔係有爭取民主到底嘅最大決心，我一定會以呢一點作為武器，消磨大家嘅抗爭意志<br />\n<br />\n我哋目標係咩<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"6f8f1814cb0ce224d4a16336296965607df23836","tid":1980850,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T10:33:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5167d68698a26e0362e661494b9ea6e53d65c9e6","tid":1980850,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96e4cae8b51ce40519775c386144e1bd799bc796","tid":1980850,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T10:37:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51494d5bf7db9e0f5a4ce3ccdc521cd74c970dc9","tid":1980850,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"你尊重佢係一位為民主奮戰多年嘅老人家?<br />\n<br />\n但係你知唔知佢有份大力推動香港<del>回歸</del>支殖?"},{"pid":"6c762a12f2eb5ec169b3fd4153a9dac923136786","tid":1980850,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51494d5bf7db9e0f5a4ce3ccdc521cd74c970dc9","tid":1980850,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"你尊重佢係一位為民主奮戰多年嘅老人家?<br />\n<br />\n但係你知唔知佢有份大力推動香港<del>回歸</del>