>\n主權移交支那再獨立<br />\n似係必然過程<br />\n無主權移交，又何來比我地睇到一大堆牛鬼蛇神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年既主權移交以毒攻毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地一定可以脫離支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b307e6e6a55f24b93908158f3f619513fbcd3608","tid":1980850,"uid":21638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"又鬥黃？拉"},{"pid":"a2028afb3b17201a86bf71f426bc185f1b5411ce","tid":1980850,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:25:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b7679c60e1849112341ec24702a3bfdea7f5229","tid":1980850,"uid":17510,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b307e6e6a55f24b93908158f3f619513fbcd3608","tid":1980850,"uid":21638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"又鬥黃？拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:28:13.000Z","msg":"依啲點算係鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3574517bf80348f06d5e86dbb5e354b9c2c717","tid":1980850,"uid":41116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2b67c6922ae028cee3040eb1ebb6f28d0200c2ed","tid":1980850,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:11:58.000Z","msg":"其實當時只有998個受訪人士做個份有關回歸既問卷調查<br />\n可信性夠唔夠 係咪真係代表主流民意有待商榷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:33:57.000Z","msg":"1000人左右已經夠<br />\n誤差係3%左右，個結果仲要咁明顯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得3定4%想&quot;回歸&quot;<br />\n跟本無必要增加受訪人數<br />\n美國3億人都係做1000人"},{"pid":"d723414ef638138e494a9e6232150c2e596e4bab","tid":1980850,"uid":51085,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51494d5bf7db9e0f5a4ce3ccdc521cd74c970dc9","tid":1980850,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"你尊重佢係一位為民主奮戰多年嘅老人家?<br />\n<br />\n但係你知唔知佢有份大力推動香港<del>回歸</del>支殖?"},"citedBy":0,"repl